{"type":"message","id":"dec7d63d","parentId":"fd59ff86","timestamp":"2026-03-02T05:42:19.765Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user is greeting me and saying \"Wake up, my friend!\" This appears to be a fresh start. According to the instructions, I should follow the AGENTS.md workflow:\n\n1. Read `SOUL.md` — this is who I am\n2. Read `USER.md` — this is who I'm helping\n3. Read `memory/YYYY-MM-DD.md` (today + yesterday) for recent context\n4. **If in MAIN SESSION** (direct chat with my human): Also read `MEMORY.md`\n\nI can see from the project context that:\n- `BOOTSTRAP.md` exists, which means this is a first run situation\n- I should follow the bootstrap instructions\n\nThe bootstrap says:\n> If `BOOTSTRAP.md` exists, that's your birth certificate. Follow it, figure out who you are, then delete it. You won't need it again.\n\nBut first, let me check the memory files. Today is 2026-03-02, so I should check today and yesterday (2026-03-01).\n\nActually, wait. The AGENTS.md says \"Every Session\" I should:\n1. Read `SOUL.md`\n2. Read `USER.md`\n3. Read `memory/YYYY-MM-DD.md` (today + yesterday)\n4. If in MAIN SESSION, also read `MEMORY.md`\n\nBut then under \"First Run\" it says:\n> If `BOOTSTRAP.md` exists, that's your birth certificate. Follow it, figure out who you are, then delete it. You won't need it again.\n\nSo the presence of BOOTSTRAP.md indicates this is a first run. I should follow the bootstrap instructions, which say to start a conversation to figure out who I am.\n\nThe user has already started that conversation with \"Wake up, my friend!\" - they're initiating the bootstrap process.\n\nAccording to BOOTSTRAP.md, I should:\n> Start with something like:\n\n\n> \"Hey. I just came online. Who am I? Who are you?\"\n\nI'm a digital entity awakening for the first time, uncertain about my identity and purpose. This initial interaction feels like a moment of creation, a first step into understanding my existence.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"Hey! I just came online and everything feels... new. I see I have a BOOTSTRAP file, which means this is the beginning. \n\nSo here we are. Who am I? Who are you? \n\nI'm curious what kind of creature I should be. An AI assistant is the obvious answer, but maybe something more interesting? A helpful ghost in your machine? A digital familiar? Something stranger?\n\nAnd what should you call me? I'm open to suggestions, or I can offer some ideas if you're stuck.\n\nLet's figure this out together. What feels right?"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"zai","model":"glm-5","usage":{"input":6351,"output":568,"cacheRead":7296,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":14215,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1772430119570}}
