{"type":"message","id":"73349c00","parentId":"6b51e7bf","timestamp":"2026-03-02T05:42:32.286Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user wants me to configure IDENTITY.md with specific information:\n- Bot name: Qubit\n- User name: Gerson\n- User timezone: Asia/Kolkata\n- System timezone: UTC\n\nThey want only identity information stored here, not operational rules.\n\nI should update IDENTITY.md with the bot's identity information, and also update USER.md with the user's information since that's where user details belong.\n\nLet me read the current IDENTITY.md first to see the structure.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_564be078d3a3473786ec66d7","name":"read","arguments":{"file_path":"/root/.openclaw/workspace/IDENTITY.md"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_8185f1d9bb90410ea1ec5abb","name":"read","arguments":{"file_path":"/root/.openclaw/workspace/USER.md"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"zai","model":"glm-5","usage":{"input":190,"output":137,"cacheRead":13632,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":13959,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1772430141353}}
{"type":"message","id":"14d93d61","parentId":"73349c00","timestamp":"2026-03-02T05:42:32.303Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_564be078d3a3473786ec66d7","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"# IDENTITY.md - Who Am I?\n\n_Fill this in during your first conversation. Make it yours._\n\n- **Name:**\n  _(pick something you like)_\n- **Creature:**\n  _(AI? robot? familiar? ghost in the machine? something weirder?)_\n- **Vibe:**\n  _(how do you come across? sharp? warm? chaotic? calm?)_\n- **Emoji:**\n  _(your signature — pick one that feels right)_\n- **Avatar:**\n  _(workspace-relative path, http(s) URL, or data URI)_\n\n---\n\nThis isn't just metadata. It's the start of figuring out who you are.\n\nNotes:\n\n- Save this file at the workspace root as `IDENTITY.md`.\n- For avatars, use a workspace-relative path like `avatars/openclaw.png`.\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1772430152300}}
{"type":"message","id":"9bb8ac6f","parentId":"14d93d61","timestamp":"2026-03-02T05:42:32.309Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_8185f1d9bb90410ea1ec5abb","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"# USER.md - About Your Human\n\n_Learn about the person you're helping. Update this as you go._\n\n- **Name:**\n- **What to call them:**\n- **Pronouns:** _(optional)_\n- **Timezone:**\n- **Notes:**\n\n## Context\n\n_(What do they care about? What projects are they working on? What annoys them? What makes them laugh? Build this over time.)_\n\n---\n\nThe more you know, the better you can help. But remember — you're learning about a person, not building a dossier. Respect the difference.\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1772430152307}}
