{"type":"message","id":"5a2d7b21","parentId":"4cdcdc4f","timestamp":"2026-03-02T05:43:59.133Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Done. Timezone doctrine is now in TOOLS.md, short and rule-based as requested.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"Done. `TOOLS.md` updated with timezone doctrine:\n\n| Context | Timezone |\n|---------|----------|\n| System ops / due checks | UTC |\n| User-facing timestamps | Asia/Kolkata |\n| Scheduled items | Store both UTC + IST |\n\nGot it. I'll operate in UTC internally but always surface times in your timezone."}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"zai","model":"glm-5","usage":{"input":377,"output":88,"cacheRead":15232,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":15697,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1772430232714}}
