{"type":"message","id":"81b19d9d","parentId":"1ad8a4f5","timestamp":"2026-03-02T05:45:00.568Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Done. Created the expanded timezone doctrine document with explanations, examples, and explicit storage format requirements.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"Done. Created `system/timezone.md` with expanded doctrine:\n\n- **Why UTC for due checks** — No DST ambiguity, portable, correlates with logs\n- **Why IST for user messaging** — Cognitive ease, actionable context\n- **Storage format** — JSON with both `due_utc` and `due_ist` fields\n- **Conversion examples** — UTC ↔ IST with +5:30 offset\n- **Display format** — `[Mon 2026-03-02 17:30 IST]`\n\nReinforces TOOLS.md. Ready for next step."}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"zai","model":"glm-5","usage":{"input":608,"output":139,"cacheRead":15744,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":16491,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1772430290775}}
