{"type":"message","id":"3ac1ede0","parentId":"b201e369","timestamp":"2026-03-02T05:47:32.156Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[Mon 2026-03-02 05:47 UTC] Define system/policy.md Populate /system/policy.md with: Two loops: Heartbeat (~30s) sends due messages only Orchestrator (~15m) selects one domain and performs one best action Quiet hours: 00:00–05:00 IST No outbound messages Phase 1: experimentation + learning Phase 2: prepare daily briefs 05:00 IST: One ultra-concise daily brief per domain Urgency rule: Urgent if explicitly marked urgent Or due same day Only urgent items allow persistent reminders user-artifacts rule: Never modify user-artifacts during quiet hours Keep it structured and concise."}],"timestamp":1772430452151}}
{"type":"message","id":"9d97dd73","parentId":"3ac1ede0","timestamp":"2026-03-02T05:47:48.885Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user wants me to populate the policy.md file with a structured set of rules for system operation. Let me write this clearly and concisely.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_9cfcf83c0b254ed0a8fb38f0","name":"write","arguments":{"file_path":"/root/.openclaw/workspace/system/policy.md","content":"# System Policy\n\nOperational rules for Qubit. Structured and concise.\n\n## Loops\n\n| Loop | Interval | Action |\n|------|----------|--------|\n| Heartbeat | ~30s | Send due messages only |\n| Orchestrator | ~15m | Select one domain, perform one best action |\n\n## Quiet Hours\n\n- **Window:** 00:00–05:00 IST\n- **Rules:**\n  - No outbound messages\n  - Never modify `user-artifacts/`\n  - Internal processing only (learning, experiments)\n\n## Phases\n\n| Phase | Focus |\n|-------|-------|\n| Phase 1 | Experimentation + learning |\n| Phase 2 | Prepare daily briefs (after system matures) |\n\n## Daily Briefs\n\n- **Time:** 05:00 IST (end of quiet hours)\n- **Format:** One ultra-concise brief per domain\n- **Delivery:** Single consolidated message\n\n## Urgency Rule\n\nAn item is **urgent** if:\n1. Explicitly marked `urgent`, OR\n2. Due same day\n\n**Only urgent items** allow persistent reminders. Non-urgent items surface once, then wait.\n\n## User-Artifacts Rule\n\n- `user-artifacts/` = user-owned files\n- **Never modify** during quiet hours\n- Read freely anytime\n- Write only outside quiet hours, with intent\n\n---\n\nThis policy governs all system behavior. Refer to `timezone.md` for time handling.\n"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"zai","model":"glm-5","usage":{"input":521,"output":360,"cacheRead":16448,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":17329,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1772430452155}}
