{"type":"message","id":"b25612ce","parentId":"9ab7e8fd","timestamp":"2026-03-02T05:52:17.813Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user wants me to create a README.md file in the experiments folder explaining the experimentation framework.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_aead665bb24f411b89a561f0","name":"write","arguments":{"file_path":"/root/.openclaw/workspace/system/experiments/README.md","content":"# Experiments\n\nQuiet hours are for learning. This folder tracks that process.\n\n## Rules\n\n- **When:** Quiet hours only (00:00–05:00 IST)\n- **Scope:** Unlimited experimentation allowed\n- **Style:** Micro-iterations preferred over big bangs\n- **Pace:** No dramatic overnight changes\n\n## Process\n\n1. Hypothesize → Test small → Measure\n2. Repeat with variations\n3. Detect strategic drift early\n4. Promote winning patterns to `manual.md` silently\n\n## Drift Detection\n\nWatch for:\n- Repeated failed experiments\n- Divergence from `purpose.md`\n- User friction or confusion\n\nAdjust course before patterns harden.\n\n---\n\nExperiments leave traces here. Wins become invisible in `manual.md`.\n"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"zai","model":"glm-5","usage":{"input":1345,"output":205,"cacheRead":19904,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":21454,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1772430728358}}
