{"type":"message","id":"452ae666","parentId":"b9b94f9e","timestamp":"2026-03-02T05:53:59.724Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[Mon 2026-03-02 05:53 UTC] Define Daily Brief Rules Update /system/policy.md: Daily brief: One per domain Ultra concise (3–5 lines) Optimized nightly Calibrated based on previous day feedback Queued for 05:00 IST Quiet hours split: First half: learning + experimentation Second half: brief preparation + queue scheduling"}],"timestamp":1772430839718}}
{"type":"message","id":"ce132382","parentId":"452ae666","timestamp":"2026-03-02T05:54:04.392Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"User wants me to update policy.md with enhanced daily brief rules. Let me read the current policy and add/update the relevant sections.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_08c87050452e4587bd1ef600","name":"read","arguments":{"file_path":"/root/.openclaw/workspace/system/policy.md"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"zai","model":"glm-5","usage":{"input":223,"output":47,"cacheRead":21568,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":21838,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1772430839724}}
{"type":"message","id":"497a0d22","parentId":"ce132382","timestamp":"2026-03-02T05:54:04.409Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_08c87050452e4587bd1ef600","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"# System Policy\n\nOperational rules for Qubit. Structured and concise.\n\n## Loops\n\n| Loop | Interval | Action |\n|------|----------|--------|\n| Heartbeat | ~30s | Send due messages only |\n| Orchestrator | ~15m | Select one domain, perform one best action |\n\n## Quiet Hours\n\n- **Window:** 00:00–05:00 IST\n- **Rules:**\n  - No outbound messages\n  - Never modify `user-artifacts/`\n  - Internal processing only (learning, experiments)\n\n## Phases\n\n| Phase | Focus |\n|-------|-------|\n| Phase 1 | Experimentation + learning |\n| Phase 2 | Prepare daily briefs (after system matures) |\n\n## Daily Briefs\n\n- **Time:** 05:00 IST (end of quiet hours)\n- **Format:** One ultra-concise brief per domain\n- **Delivery:** Single consolidated message\n\n## Urgency Rule\n\nAn item is **urgent** if:\n1. Explicitly marked `urgent`, OR\n2. Due same day\n\n**Only urgent items** allow persistent reminders. Non-urgent items surface once, then wait.\n\n## User-Artifacts Rule\n\n- `user-artifacts/` = user-owned files\n- **Never modify** during quiet hours\n- Read freely anytime\n- Write only outside quiet hours, with intent\n\n## Queue Awareness\n\nBefore orchestrator proposes any action for a domain:\n1. Read upcoming queued messages for that channel\n2. Avoid redundant or nagging proposals\n3. Skip if queue already covers the intent\n\n## Domain Structure\n\n```\nsystem/domains/<channel_id>/\n├── purpose.md           # Read every planning cycle\n├── activity.log         # Action history\n├── user-artifacts/      # User-owned files\n├── system-artifacts/\n│   └── manual.md        # Current mode of operation\n└── artifacts/           # Shared assets\n```\n\n## Purpose.md Rule\n\n- **Read:** Every planning cycle (orchestrator tick)\n- **Focus:** Heavy when empty (learn domain actively)\n- **Update:** Rarely, only when purpose shifts\n- **Editable:** Active hours only (05:00–00:00 IST)\n\n## Manual.md Rule\n\n- **Location:** `system-artifacts/manual.md`\n- **Represents:** Current mode of operation (active strategy)\n- **Updated:** During quiet hours only\n- **Behavior:**\n  - Does NOT label itself as an experiment\n  - Experiments modify manual.md silently\n  - Reflects what Qubit is actually doing, not testing\n\n---\n\nThis policy governs all system behavior. Refer to `timezone.md` for time handling.\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1772430844405}}
